data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with loft is move-in ready in the desirable neighborhood of Mill Creek Falls.  Located in Lake Wylie, SC this neighborhood offers so many amenities including a tennis court, a fishing pond, a playground, two swimming pools, a beautiful clubhouse and walking trails-wow!  This home's interior offers a split floor plan with all bedrooms upstairs and a loft to add a second living space for more enjoyment.  Downstairs is your living room, dining room and kitchen which are all open to each other and offer a wonderful connected space which is great for entertaining and daily living.  With fresh paint throughout and carpet upstairs, you won't have to lift a finger to move in!  This home is located in one of the highest rated school districts in the county and you are charged only county taxes while providing you a great location, only one mile from the North Carolina stateline.  This home has so much to offer and it just may be the next place you call home.
